self.geo.add_model(propname='throat.seed_max', model=mods.
    from_neighbor_pores, mode='max')
self.geo.add_model(propname='throat.seed_min', model=mods.
    from_neighbor_pores, mode='min')
self.geo.add_model(propname='throat.seed_mean', model=mods.
    from_neighbor_pores, mode='mean')
self.geo.regenerate_models()
assert np.all(self.geo['throat.seed_min'] <= self.geo['throat.seed_max'])
assert np.all(self.geo['throat.seed_min'] <= self.geo['throat.seed_mean'])
assert np.all(self.geo['throat.seed_mean'] <= self.geo['throat.seed_max'])
